# Theme Configuration

## Colors

```scss
// Palette (optional, project-specific)
$pale: #fbf8f3;
$mist: #f7f1e8;
$sand: #eae2d7;
$muted: #8c807d;
$deep: #362925;
$magento: #671e3a;

// Brand
$primary-color: #1f2261;
$secondary-color: #fdba00;
$success-color: #33b469;
$info-color: #ebbc2e;
$warning-color: #ebbc2e;

// Typography
$body-color: #080c11;
$heading-color: inherit;
$link-color: $body-color;
$link-hover-color: inherit;
```

## Typography

```scss
$serif-font-family: 'Libre Baskerville', serif;
$sans-serif-font-family: 'Geist', -apple-system, sans-serif;
$body-font-size: rem-calc(16);
$body-font-family: $sans-serif-font-family;
$heading-font-family: $serif-font-family;
```

### Heading Scale (fluid)

```scss
h1: fluid(32, 48)    h2: fluid(24, 40)    h3: fluid(20, 32)
h4: fluid(18, 22)    h5: fluid(16, 18)    h6: fluid(14, 16)
```

### Text Utility Scale (fluid)

```scss
text(small):  fluid(12, 14)
text(medium): fluid(14, 16)
```

## Breakpoints

```scss
$xs: 0px      $ph: 375px    $sm: 576px
$md: 768px    $lg: 1024px   $xl: 1200px
$xxl: 1400px
```

## Container

```scss
// Max-widths by breakpoint:
// ph/sm: 100vw, md: 95vw, lg/xl/xxl: 93vw, xxl: 80rem (1280px)
// Padding: fluid(20, 40)  ($container-padding-x)
```

## Section Spacing Classes

| Class                                            | Value             |
| ------------------------------------------------ | ----------------- |
| `.spacing-top-small` / `.spacing-bottom-small`   | `fluid(20, 40)`   |
| `.spacing-top-medium` / `.spacing-bottom-medium` | `fluid(40, 70)`   |
| `.spacing-top-large` / `.spacing-bottom-large`   | `fluid(70, 140)`  |
| `.spacing-top-xlarge` / `.spacing-bottom-xlarge` | `fluid(100, 160)` |

## PHP Constants (from ACF Options)

```php
DEFAULT_THUMBNAIL_ID   // Fallback featured image
PAGE_404_ID            // Custom 404 page ID
PAGE_SEARCH_ID         // Search results page ID
```
